a place
of exception

   Known internationally for the richness of its concretions (especially
   the very rare aragonite and eccentric crystals), the Clamouse makes for
   a magical out-of-time journey … Come and enjoy the diversity of its
   subterranean landscapes that are near unique in Europe ! Whether for a
   solo visit or with family or friends, our team is on hand to help you
   discover the treasures of the Clamouse.
   Hours Prices

Original
activities

   The team invites you to discover the Clamouse in a totally different
   way with surprising activities !
   The speleopark, 2 sports course for intense sensation, and an escape
   game in the heart of the Cave.
   Let's go !
   Discover the activities

The pass
offers

   This summer, thanks to our partners at the LET’S GOrges Collective,
   discover the Gorges of the Hérault with our outdoor activities
   (canoeing, climbing, water hiking) coupled with the Clamouse Cave and
   the Speleopark for a tailor-made day that mixes nature, culture and
   sports activities.
   Call us at +33 (0)4 67 57 71 05

